Mobile,Automated,Systems,is,a,mobile,telecommunications,provider,that,automates,the,process,of,sending,and,receiving,bulk,text,alerts,With,the,Mobile,Automated,System,s,API,developers,can,interface,with,the,Mobile,Automated,Systems,messaging,gateway,from,any,application,or,website,Using,the,API,to,access,this,portal,SMS,campaigns,can,be,created,scheduled,and,launched,The,API,parameters,include,naming,recipients,the,sender,ID,to,be,displayed,and,the,text,message,to,be,sent,Basic,account,maintenance,can,be,performed,as,the,API,allows,the,ability,to,check,account,balance,Users,are,authenticated,according,to,the,username,and,password,sent,with,the,corresponding,parameters